  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AzkabanCompactionJobLauncher
    A class for launching a Gobblin MR job for compaction through Azkaban.
    AzkabanGobblinDaemon
    Wrapper of SchedulerDaemon, specially used by Azkaban to launch a job scheduler daemon.
    AzkabanGobblinYarnAppLauncher
    A utility class for launching a Gobblin application on Yarn through Azkaban.
    AzkabanIntegrationTestLauncher
    This class launches the TestHarness framework using Azkaban Created by spyne on 6/8/15.
    AzkabanJobLauncher
    A utility class for launching a Gobblin Hadoop MR job through Azkaban.
    AzkabanStateStoreCleanerJob
    A utility class for running the StateStoreCleaner on Azkaban.
    AzkabanTags
    Utility class for collecting metadata specific to a Azkaban runtime environment.
